column8: Cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers, most likely during the morning and afternoon. Snow falling above 1100 metres. Winds south to southwesterly 15 to 25 km/h turning east to southeasterly 25 to 35 km/h during the morning and early afternoon. Daytime maximum temperatures between 7 and 13.

Cloudy. High (70%) chance of showers about the ranges, medium (40%) chance elsewhere. Snow falling above 1200 metres. Winds easterly 25 to 40 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to between 4 and 9 with daytime temperatures reaching between 9 and 15.

Cloudy. High (80%) chance of showers. Snow falling above 1400 metres. Winds easterly 25 to 35 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to between 4 and 9 with daytime temperatures reaching between 11 and 15.

Partly cloudy. Areas of morning fog in the east. High (70%) chance of showers, most likely in the afternoon and evening. The chance of a thunderstorm in the late morning and afternoon. Winds easterly 15 to 25 km/h. Overnight temperatures falling to between 5 and 10 with daytime temperatures reaching between 15 and 19.
